WEBVTT

20:22.971 --> 20:25.307
Where do you think you're going?

21:03.679 --> 21:05.097
Get the Elephant.

41:01.667 --> 41:02.918
Still alive.

41:04.503 --> 41:06.172
But he is barely breathing.

41:08.007 --> 41:11.010
More of this, he will die.

41:24.982 --> 41:26.901
Send him to Kamchatka!

41:34.116 --> 41:37.620
I never knew you to be generous.

41:39.246 --> 41:41.749
You clearly do not know Kamchatka, Doctor.

41:43.584 --> 41:46.295
This man does not deserve
the peace of death.

41:48.506 --> 41:49.840
So I have sent him...

41:51.258 --> 41:52.384
to Hell.

54:15.001 --> 54:17.420
You are no longer men.

54:19.631 --> 54:21.466
You are cogs in a machine.

54:21.549 --> 54:25.845
A machine in service
of our great Motherland.

54:29.140 --> 54:32.185
And if you are foolish enough
to attempt escape,

54:33.853 --> 54:35.730
you will be hunted down.

54:37.274 --> 54:38.692
You will be captured.

54:39.567 --> 54:42.028
And then you will suffer greatly

54:42.112 --> 54:44.781
as you perform your final act

54:44.864 --> 54:46.533
for the Motherland.

54:47.117 --> 54:49.995
There will be no second chances.
